
1.reinterpret_cast<type> (expr)
  用于指针之间的转换


2.void* align(size_t alignment,size_t size,void*& ptr,size_t& space)
  该函数在ptr指向的大小为space的内存中进行对齐方式的调整，将ptr开始的size大小的数据调整为按alignment对齐
  1)alignment 
    Requested alignment,in bytes
  2)size
    Size of element to be aligned,in bytes
  3)ptr
    value-result
    It points to contigunuous storage of at least space bytes
  4)space
    value-result
    Maximum size of the buffer to consider for alignment
  
